1
00:00:25,250 --> 00:00:32,210
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="33"><font face="Georgia"><font color="#9eccf8">Beyond Journey's End</font></font></font></b></font>

2
00:01:29,990 --> 00:01:32,990
<font face="Times New Roman">{\an7}<font color="#f7fffa">Episode 35: The Divine Revolte</font></font>

3
00:01:37,850 --> 00:01:41,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Genau's partner died 
in battle the other day.</font>

4
00:01:42,210 --> 00:01:47,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you'll be slaying demons together 
on the Northern Plateau for a while.</font>

5
00:01:49,410 --> 00:01:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I look forward to working 
with you, Mr. Genau.</font>

6
00:01:54,130 --> 00:01:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Northern Plateau is as dangerous</font>

7
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:59,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as you'd expect the farthest 
reaches of the north to be.</font>

8
00:01:59,540 --> 00:02:01,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't hold me back.</font>

9
00:02:05,760 --> 00:02:06,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now shake hands.</font>

10
00:02:20,650 --> 00:02:24,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Methode, do you think 
you are a good person?</font>

11
00:02:26,420 --> 00:02:28,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't understand what you're saying.</font>

12
00:02:30,780 --> 00:02:33,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My previous partner was a good person.</font>

13
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The exact opposite of me.</font>

14
00:02:37,060 --> 00:02:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'd try his hardest 
for complete strangers.</font>

15
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was always so boisterous, 
so full of smiles.</font>

16
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:52,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He treated me as casually 
as an old friend,</font>

17
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and his personality naturally 
drew people to him.</font>

18
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:07,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was a fool.</font>

19
00:03:20,500 --> 00:03:22,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He died protecting a child.</font>

20
00:03:25,490 --> 00:03:28,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because of that, 
we failed to kill the demon.</font>

21
00:03:30,670 --> 00:03:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd never do anything so stupid.</font>

22
00:03:36,650 --> 00:03:38,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've forsaken countless people already.</font>

23
00:03:40,220 --> 00:03:42,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why me?</font>

24
00:03:44,050 --> 00:03:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

25
00:03:45,500 --> 00:03:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why was I chosen to work with you?</font>

26
00:03:48,770 --> 00:03:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows? It was Ms. Serie's decision.</font>

27
00:03:55,820 --> 00:04:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I can say is that first-class mages 
who get dispatched to the Northern Plateau</font>

28
00:04:02,300 --> 00:04:05,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are usually the type that loves fighting 
more than three meals a day.</font>

29
00:04:08,090 --> 00:04:09,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It certainly is strange.</font>

30
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:13,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why you, and not Übel?</font>

31
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:19,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, no decent 
person likes fighting.</font>

32
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't end up like me.</font>

33
00:04:30,690 --> 00:04:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's share what information we have 
before we begin our search.</font>

34
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

35
00:04:36,980 --> 00:04:40,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Based on traces of magic 
and other evidence,</font>

36
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there are four primary demons 
who attacked the village.</font>

37
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All four have vanished from the area.</font>

38
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:48,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Four? That's a lot.</font>

39
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:52,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One of them was a demon general.</font>

40
00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:55,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It killed the knights with four swords.</font>

41
00:05:00,230 --> 00:05:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly is a demon general?</font>

42
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:05,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A highly skilled and experienced 
demon warrior.</font>

43
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:09,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They fight by enhancing their physical 
capabilities with powerful magic.</font>

44
00:05:10,390 --> 00:05:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some are devotees who spend hundreds 
of years perfecting their martial skills.</font>

45
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some of the generals in the Demon King's 
army were far stronger than Eisen.</font>

46
00:05:20,330 --> 00:05:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

47
00:05:21,830 --> 00:05:27,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, it's likely that it has 
a far-from-human appearance.</font>

48
00:05:27,580 --> 00:05:30,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that bad?</font>

49
00:05:30,730 --> 00:05:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you ever fought an expert swordsman 
who wields four swords at once?</font>

50
00:05:35,890 --> 00:05:37,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not.</font>

51
00:05:37,550 --> 00:05:39,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me neither.</font>

52
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's probably why the knights lost.</font>

53
00:05:49,810 --> 00:05:51,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Revolte.</font>

54
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:55,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our prey has been caught in our net.</font>

55
00:05:55,510 --> 00:05:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're a tasty meal, rich in mana.</font>

56
00:05:58,040 --> 00:06:00,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One warrior, three mages.</font>

57
00:06:00,580 --> 00:06:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three are first-class.</font>

58
00:06:04,450 --> 00:06:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can handle that many.</font>

59
00:06:07,310 --> 00:06:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we attack?</font>

60
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

61
00:06:11,310 --> 00:06:13,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have a bad feeling about them.</font>

62
00:06:13,620 --> 00:06:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll wait for them to split up.</font>

63
00:06:15,970 --> 00:06:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think they will, Lord Revolte? 
They seemed rather guarded.</font>

64
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They will.</font>

65
00:06:30,470 --> 00:06:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why we provoked them 
by killing all those people.</font>

66
00:06:35,740 --> 00:06:41,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the course of destroying all these 
villages on the Northern Plateau,</font>

67
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've noticed something.</font>

68
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ooh, what is it?</font>

69
00:06:49,310 --> 00:06:52,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go look for the demons.</font>

70
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll head to the abandoned fort 
to the north first.</font>

71
00:06:57,260 --> 00:07:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Demons often hide out 
in places like that.</font>

72
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait.</font>

73
00:07:06,540 --> 00:07:09,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Chivalric Order of Norm 
still needs to collect the bodies.</font>

74
00:07:09,270 --> 00:07:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone should stay 
in the village until then.</font>

75
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:15,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll remain behind.</font>

76
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Humans have a habit of remaining 
in villages to protect their corpses.</font>

77
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How interesting. Why do they do that?</font>

78
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't need to know the reason.</font>

79
00:07:27,710 --> 00:07:32,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder why, though. 
I'm so very, very curious.</font>

80
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're interested in humans? 
You're a strange one.</font>

81
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:43,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Humans sometimes behave 
illogically and irrationally.</font>

82
00:07:43,220 --> 00:07:45,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to know why they do that.</font>

83
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:49,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's just how they are. 
There's nothing more to it.</font>

84
00:07:49,950 --> 00:07:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't need to know why.</font>

85
00:07:54,500 --> 00:08:01,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it, I've heard of an 
eccentric demon who studies humanity.</font>

86
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:06,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Tell me more about them, please!</font>

87
00:08:06,950 --> 00:08:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you think it will be 
of use to you, I will.</font>

88
00:08:10,470 --> 00:08:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will? Then it's a promise, 
Lord Revolte!</font>

89
00:08:16,140 --> 00:08:18,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll stay by yourself?</font>

90
00:08:18,390 --> 00:08:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They shouldn't be much longer.</font>

91
00:08:21,710 --> 00:08:26,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll meet up with you once the 
Order has collected the bodies.</font>

92
00:08:26,820 --> 00:08:27,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine.</font>

93
00:08:35,180 --> 00:08:36,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll stay, too.</font>

94
00:08:37,590 --> 00:08:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you stupid?</font>

95
00:08:39,830 --> 00:08:42,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your party is heading out to fight demons.</font>

96
00:08:42,660 --> 00:08:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will they do without a front-liner?</font>

97
00:08:44,670 --> 00:08:46,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same goes for you.</font>

98
00:08:46,910 --> 00:08:49,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if the demons return to the village?</font>

99
00:08:49,690 --> 00:08:51,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't be a problem.</font>

100
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can fight well enough 
without a front-liner.</font>

101
00:08:54,570 --> 00:08:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So can Frieren and the others.</font>

102
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's only so much 
we can handle, though.</font>

103
00:08:59,340 --> 00:09:02,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if things look bad, 
you can run, right?</font>

104
00:09:02,680 --> 00:09:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess so.</font>

105
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't run away, though. 
You'd be abandoning the village.</font>

106
00:09:10,210 --> 00:09:13,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stark. All that's left here is the dead.</font>

107
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:17,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's who you're staying 
to protect, right?</font>

108
00:09:20,230 --> 00:09:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Suit yourself.</font>

109
00:09:36,340 --> 00:09:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stark, you're a good person.</font>

110
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:43,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've known people like you.</font>

111
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:45,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They tend not to live long.</font>

112
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:51,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem like a good person to me, too.</font>

113
00:09:54,140 --> 00:09:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're still trying to defend the village,
even after it's been destroyed.</font>

114
00:09:58,910 --> 00:10:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't do that.</font>

115
00:10:07,330 --> 00:10:09,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not a good person.</font>

116
00:10:10,250 --> 00:10:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quite the opposite.</font>

117
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've done whatever it took to 
bring peace to the northern lands.</font>

118
00:10:18,880 --> 00:10:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've killed and forsaken many people.</font>

119
00:10:24,770 --> 00:10:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps this is what I deserve.</font>

120
00:10:27,350 --> 00:10:29,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You get used to people dying, you know.</font>

121
00:10:32,910 --> 00:10:35,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't feel even slightly sad.</font>

122
00:10:35,660 --> 00:10:38,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My hometown's been destroyed, 
but I feel nothing.</font>

123
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm only staying in this village 
because I thought I should.</font>

124
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:48,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've forsaken so many in the past,</font>

125
00:10:49,850 --> 00:10:52,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so what am I even doing?</font>

126
00:10:57,920 --> 00:11:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stark, many people call 
the Northern Plateau home.</font>

127
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From now on, avoid using 
long-range detection.</font>

128
00:11:18,180 --> 00:11:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they're skilled, they 
can trace it back to us.</font>

129
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:21,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

130
00:11:22,160 --> 00:11:26,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, we still have a ways 
to go before we reach the fort.</font>

131
00:11:26,510 --> 00:11:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's talk while we walk.</font>

132
00:11:29,570 --> 00:11:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we be doing that?</font>

133
00:11:31,390 --> 00:11:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's important to ease the tension.</font>

134
00:11:36,980 --> 00:11:38,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She looks so careless.</font>

135
00:11:41,670 --> 00:11:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, communication improves teamwork.</font>

136
00:11:45,580 --> 00:11:47,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet you didn't know that.</font>

137
00:11:47,410 --> 00:11:48,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

138
00:11:49,180 --> 00:11:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, Ms. Frieren, may I pet you?</font>

139
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is she actually saying that 
with a straight face?</font>

140
00:11:56,290 --> 00:12:01,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love giving headpats to small girls,</font>

141
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:04,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but Ms. Serie doesn't let me do it often.</font>

142
00:12:05,450 --> 00:12:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only that, but she always 
looks so displeased when I do.</font>

143
00:12:09,170 --> 00:12:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would, too.</font>

144
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:16,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And besides, I'm the older 
one here by far, Methode.</font>

145
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't suffer headpats 
from the likes of you.</font>

146
00:12:18,430 --> 00:12:21,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. Ms. Frieren 
is a mature lady.</font>

147
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:23,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't think you can casually touch her.</font>

148
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Frieren.</font>

149
00:12:28,890 --> 00:12:30,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This contains a spell</font>

150
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that prevents pieces of shell from 
falling in when cracking eggs.</font>

151
00:12:35,500 --> 00:12:37,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can pet me all you want.</font>

152
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Frieren?</font>

153
00:12:45,830 --> 00:12:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe you're allowing me 
to pet you this much.</font>

154
00:12:49,990 --> 00:12:52,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No more than ten minutes per day.</font>

155
00:12:52,730 --> 00:12:53,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

156
00:13:01,890 --> 00:13:07,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Frieren, may I hug you a little?</font>

157
00:13:07,010 --> 00:13:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Serie never let me.</font>

158
00:13:10,140 --> 00:13:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do whatever you want.</font>

159
00:13:11,830 --> 00:13:13,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever I want?!</font>

160
00:13:22,290 --> 00:13:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What?</font>

161
00:13:26,590 --> 00:13:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, stop.</font>

162
00:13:30,920 --> 00:13:33,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll tear me in half...</font>

163
00:13:38,930 --> 00:13:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this...?</font>

164
00:13:40,580 --> 00:13:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been detected. 
They know where we are.</font>

165
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:47,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's demons for you.</font>

166
00:13:47,960 --> 00:13:50,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're aggressive.</font>

167
00:13:50,540 --> 00:13:55,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They must know we're skilled mages, 
but that doesn't faze them.</font>

168
00:13:59,270 --> 00:14:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They noticed.</font>

169
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:03,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Shall we begin?</font>

170
00:14:07,430 --> 00:14:08,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nebeladora.</font>

171
00:14:14,630 --> 00:14:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a fog made of mana.</font>

172
00:14:16,660 --> 00:14:19,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're blocking our vision 
and mana detection.</font>

173
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:35,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been separated from Methode.</font>

174
00:14:36,210 --> 00:14:37,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're skilled.</font>

175
00:14:42,060 --> 00:14:43,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which one do you want?</font>

176
00:14:43,390 --> 00:14:47,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The tall one has an 
unusual aura about her.</font>

177
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:49,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She should be fun.</font>

178
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:53,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll take the other two.</font>

179
00:14:56,530 --> 00:14:59,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch out for attacks from above.</font>

180
00:14:59,570 --> 00:15:00,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Frieren.</font>

181
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

182
00:15:02,800 --> 00:15:05,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both demons were flying.</font>

183
00:15:05,770 --> 00:15:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So were the demons we fought before.</font>

184
00:15:08,720 --> 00:15:10,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's flying magic, isn't it?</font>

185
00:15:11,220 --> 00:15:12,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you.</font>

186
00:15:13,270 --> 00:15:17,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until forty years ago, 
demons ruled the skies.</font>

187
00:15:17,980 --> 00:15:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They haven't lost those skills.</font>

188
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:24,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you said demons only 
study one type of magic.</font>

189
00:15:25,780 --> 00:15:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think of walking 
as a special ability?</font>

190
00:15:30,520 --> 00:15:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the same principle.</font>

191
00:15:32,670 --> 00:15:36,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To demons, flying magic isn't even magic.</font>

192
00:15:37,180 --> 00:15:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why this is a common sight 
when fighting them.</font>

193
00:15:42,910 --> 00:15:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As I thought, they're 
accustomed to battle.</font>

194
00:15:46,340 --> 00:15:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They fight like members 
of the Demon King's army.</font>

195
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:03,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Methode has engaged the enemy.</font>

196
00:16:03,730 --> 00:16:06,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fern, you'll handle the fighting.</font>

197
00:16:06,690 --> 00:16:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

198
00:16:08,480 --> 00:16:11,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This job was assigned 
to the first-class mages.</font>

199
00:16:12,180 --> 00:16:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the first-class mage here.</font>

200
00:16:15,340 --> 00:16:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Frieren, is now 
really the time for that?</font>

201
00:16:18,090 --> 00:16:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It won't be a problem. You can beat him.</font>

202
00:16:30,310 --> 00:16:31,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See?</font>

203
00:16:32,230 --> 00:16:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

204
00:16:35,130 --> 00:16:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was just a fluke.</font>

205
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only reacted in time 
because you pointed.</font>

206
00:16:42,310 --> 00:16:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't detect his attack at all.</font>

207
00:16:49,890 --> 00:16:52,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's better than me.</font>

208
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I disagree.</font>

209
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not many first-class mages are as 
dedicated to the fundamentals as you.</font>

210
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:04,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right. You can beat him.</font>

211
00:17:14,740 --> 00:17:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I caught some fish. 
How about a late-night snack?</font>

212
00:17:19,110 --> 00:17:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll pass. Methode will be angry with me.</font>

213
00:17:22,860 --> 00:17:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She says it's unhealthy 
to eat late at night.</font>

214
00:17:25,380 --> 00:17:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah? More for me, then.</font>

215
00:17:32,110 --> 00:17:35,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always get hungry at this hour.</font>

216
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell Fern.</font>

217
00:17:41,660 --> 00:17:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

218
00:17:47,260 --> 00:17:49,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem to be dealing with a lot, too.</font>

219
00:17:55,540 --> 00:17:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Genau.</font>

220
00:17:58,060 --> 00:18:01,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know the demon who attacked 
this village, don't you?</font>

221
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:05,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Demons that fight with four 
swords are hardly common.</font>

222
00:18:07,480 --> 00:18:12,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Divine Revolte is the 
demon who killed my partner.</font>

223
00:18:15,130 --> 00:18:17,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a grandiose name.</font>

224
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It comes from the four swords 
he created using magic.</font>

225
00:18:23,900 --> 00:18:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He can freely change 
the weight of his swords.</font>

226
00:18:28,120 --> 00:18:31,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes they're sharp 
and light as a feather.</font>

227
00:18:31,460 --> 00:18:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes they're as heavy as a boulder.</font>

228
00:18:35,160 --> 00:18:38,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're called the Divine Cleaving Swords,</font>

229
00:18:38,690 --> 00:18:41,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">after the blade that split mountains 
during mythical times.</font>

230
00:18:41,870 --> 00:18:46,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So they're both light and sharp 
and unbelievably heavy.</font>

231
00:18:47,170 --> 00:18:49,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's contradictory, isn't it?</font>

232
00:18:50,260 --> 00:18:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Magic can create objects 
that shouldn't exist.</font>

233
00:18:54,970 --> 00:18:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In particular, weapons made from magic 
are the embodiment of murderous intent.</font>

234
00:19:00,230 --> 00:19:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Demons that create such 
weapons kill many people—</font>

235
00:19:04,730 --> 00:19:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">far more than necessary, 
as if to test them.</font>

236
00:19:15,070 --> 00:19:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stark.</font>

237
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. It's the enemy.</font>

238
00:19:23,420 --> 00:19:24,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fast.</font>

239
00:19:25,650 --> 00:19:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here it comes.</font>

240
00:19:57,990 --> 00:19:59,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Four swords!</font>

241
00:20:01,220 --> 00:20:04,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One warrior and one first-class mage.</font>

242
00:20:05,240 --> 00:20:09,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As I predicted, 
you're protecting the village.</font>

243
00:20:10,320 --> 00:20:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Revolte.</font>

244
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is him?</font>

245
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:16,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem to know who I am.</font>

246
00:20:17,620 --> 00:20:21,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That first-class mage 
in particular looks familiar.</font>

247
00:20:22,820 --> 00:20:24,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you?</font>

248
00:20:25,000 --> 00:20:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's begin, Stark.</font>

249
00:20:27,010 --> 00:20:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Avoid taking his attacks head-on.</font>

250
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Worst case, it could destroy you.</font>

251
00:20:34,390 --> 00:20:36,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said, who are you?</font>

252
00:20:37,010 --> 00:20:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you declare your name 
before exterminating a pest?</font>

253
00:20:42,800 --> 00:20:45,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're one twisted person.</font>

254
00:20:47,430 --> 00:20:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're both capable of speech, are we not?</font>

255
00:20:51,830 --> 00:20:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you don't wish to talk...</font>

256
00:20:59,460 --> 00:21:03,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then I, too, shall focus on 
exterminating the pests before me.</font>

257
00:21:05,170 --> 00:21:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What am I supposed to do 
if I can't take his attacks head-on?</font>

258
00:21:08,530 --> 00:21:11,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A warrior can deflect blows, can he not?</font>

259
00:21:15,940 --> 00:21:17,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but...</font>

260
00:21:28,660 --> 00:21:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't protect you like that!</font>

261
00:21:30,870 --> 00:21:33,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need protecting.</font>

262
00:21:33,530 --> 00:21:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Despite how I may seem, 
I'm skilled in close-quarters combat.</font>

263
00:21:57,000 --> 00:22:03,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Demon magic isn't the only magic capable 
of producing objects that shouldn't exist.</font>

264
00:22:04,460 --> 00:22:06,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Digardnacht.</font>

265
00:22:11,120 --> 00:22:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A spell to manipulate niello wings.</font>

266
00:22:16,570 --> 00:22:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Interesting.</font>

267
00:22:20,980 --> 00:22:25,110
<font face="Times New Roman" size="12" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="10">Translation
<font size="12">Sho Stifler

<font size="10">Editing & Typesetting
