<font size="10">Translation Check
<font size="12">Elizabeth Ellis</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font>

268
00:23:50,150 --> 00:23:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's nice to watch from afar 
once in a while.</font>

269
00:23:50,630 --> 00:23:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a bad matchup.</font>

270
00:23:51,920 --> 00:23:53,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She simply has no openings.</font>

271
00:23:52,470 --> 00:23:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't read his attacks.</font>

272
00:23:53,850 --> 00:23:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it!</font>

273
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This should be a good match.</font>

274
00:23:54,660 --> 00:23:57,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's pointless trying 
to conceal your mana and hide.</font>

275
00:23:56,460 --> 00:23:58,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I shall put you out of your misery.</font>

276
00:23:57,990 --> 00:24:00,070
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24">{\an8}<font color="#000000">Episode 36







A Magnificent End</font></font>

277
00:23:58,190 --> 00:24:00,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He met a magnificent end.</font>

